<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>The Purple Wiggle Lachlan 'Lachy' Gillespie has announced that he and his ballet dancer fiancée, Dana Stephensen have welcomed twin daughters. </p>

<p>Fans were left in complete shock - with the pair never having revealed the pregnancy -  when The Wiggles performer announced the new arrivals on Friday evening. </p>

<p>In an Instagram post, the 34-year-old shared a photo of his newborn daughters - Lulu and Lottie - resting with their mother Dana, 34, as he looked on lovingly. </p>

<p>Shock arrival! Wiggles star Lachlan 'Lachy' Gillespie has announced that he and fiancée Dana Stephensen have welcomed twin daughters. In an Instagram post shared Tuesday, the 34-year-old shared a photo of his newborn daughters - Lulu and Lottie - resting with their mother Dana, 34, as he looked on lovingly. All pictured </p>

<p>He wrote in the caption: 'Oh Lulu and Lottie, your mummy and daddy love you with all we have - you are both so beautiful - and I would love to sing to you both forever'. </p>

<p>Fans were stunned, with many voicing their complete shock at the news. </p>

<p>One person commented under the photo:  'Whaaattt! Congratulations to you both' while another added: 'WAIT WHATTTTT'. </p>

<p>Someone else added: 'Wow didn't see that coming congratulations to the three of you!'  </p>

<p>The couple announced their engagement in April with a sweet Instagram post, Lachy writing: 'On Thursday night, Dana asked me to marry her at home under a fairy light sky and a very excited little boy in a beautiful bow tie.' </p>

<p>In the photo, Lachlan was pictured cuddling up to Dana and Dana's son Jasper, four, inside a bedroom festooned with fairy lights. </p>

<p>The couple, who went public with their relationship in October, beamed with joy as they cuddled up for the milestone photo.   </p>

<p>Meanwhile, Dana shared a post on her Instagram announcing the news and revealing that Lachlan had actually proposed a month earlier. </p>

<p>'At the end of our summer holidays, I walked into the most beautiful surprise - a room filled with the most incredible flowers and Lachy singing at his piano and then asking me to marry him. It was such a surprise and so special. Our faces say it all,' she wrote next to a selfie of the couple. </p>
